                            <comment id="466208" author="adilger" created="Tue, 5 Aug 2025 00:25:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Either or both backporting the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18783&quot; title=&quot;pjdfstest test chmod 2 fails with ZFS 2.3.0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18783&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18783&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix to b2_15 to limit the filenames to 256, and/or skipping this test with a line in &lt;tt&gt;lustre/tests/except/sanity.ex&lt;/tt&gt; if the client is too old. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="466146" author="yujian" created="Mon, 4 Aug 2025 17:05:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The issue was fixed in&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18783&quot; title=&quot;pjdfstest test chmod 2 fails with ZFS 2.3.0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18783&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18783&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; on master branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="466142" author="yujian" created="Mon, 4 Aug 2025 16:53:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The failure was introduced by Lustre b2_15 build #110, which had the following two changes:&lt;br/&gt;
